The use of Gaussian mixture models and optimization techniques suggests that it could also belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-categories. The paper also deals with probabilistic modeling and convergence properties, which are relevant to the cs.SY (Systems and Control) sub-category. Finally, the use of expectation-maximization suggests that it could also belong to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category.
